{"tid":1295711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到出第六大訴求：整肅警隊，革扯違規警員","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T10:51:16.000Z","uid":79445,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8742c712fddc2978de26b3f457a3d32969187c0a","tid":1295711,"uid":79445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"大量警察16組嚴重違規行為，警方及政府須緊急嚴正交代<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/大量警察16組嚴重違規行為-警方及政府須緊急嚴正交代/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F16%E7%B5%84%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%88%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=23744b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F16%E7%B5%84%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%88%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%2F&h=1a57b70a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/大量警察16組嚴重違規行為-警方及政府須緊急嚴正交代/</a><br />\n<br />\n交代甚至道歉已經冇意思 <br />\n何況佢哋一定唔會<br />\n成個警隊敵對市民意識<br />\n已經嚴重影響佢哋執行任務嘅判斷<br />\n成個警隊文化崩壞 <br />\n唔大執一次 以後唔使講咩警民關係<br />\n<br />\n鄭立16年寫嘅 [社會課] 甚麼是警察國家？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://1988.lakoo.com/社會課-甚麼是警察國家/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1988.lakoo.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%B2-%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=d483cad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://1988.lakoo.com/社會課-甚麼是警察國家/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月已經證實哂<br />\n「警察的權力基本上已慢慢架空法庭。因為警察有權不斷滋擾不喜歡的人，同時對於自己一方政治立場者，就予以放水。」<br />\n<br />\n唔整肅只會變本加厲<br />\n<br />\n「完成了警察國家後，國家就可以不斷的通過新的法律。一些深刻的，定義含糊的法律。」<br />\n- 例如唔可以戴口罩，有睇Winter on Fire 都會記得烏克蘭政府後期有關報過類似嘅法例<br />\n<br />\n「對於「麻煩份子」，則把法律看成最嚴刻，每天都可以因為他&quot;犯法&quot;而持續用行政手段玩弄。(其實依那些法律的標準，沒有人不犯法) 不僅法治完全崩潰，而法律本身的信用也完全崩潰。」<br />\n<br />\n真係嬲到成晚瞓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MoUJTp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MoUJTp.png&h=45c037fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc5425db4a242721994fa38e603ba2296b8901f","tid":1295711,"uid":79445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"每月一次/不定期大型遊行<br />\n其餘時間零散/各區光復改善民生活動<br />\n幫大家keep住個mood<br />\n<br />\n勇武嘅突擊 突顯黑警嘅無法無天<br />\n幫民意回血<br />\n和理非嘅文宣 溫馨和諧吸引一家大細<br />\n長期戰啊各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88915bf17d1e51e6282b616761109f95f39945a0","tid":1295711,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"一早已經要求獨立調查 , 講狠77 點都未夠 612 狠"},{"pid":"a0f2049e88a7021a16458cdcaecd1b441db72600","tid":1295711,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"獨立調查完咪唔通唔跟進呀"},{"pid":"9f9aa248f8954a53c5c61673689262b30949b359","tid":1295711,"uid":79445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:47:30.000Z","msg":"調查 即係都仲有雙方各執一詞 <br />\n討價還價嘅餘地<br />\n依家證據確鑿得咁交關<br />\n<br />\n調查係要<br />\n但整肅係必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d03721e04d8641d590761e30458f112ca5c14b3","tid":1295711,"uid":154763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"－定要追究違規警員,以保警隊名聲"},{"pid":"00d3bc4124a99ee88a6769517c2f25e5f562b5d7","tid":1295711,"uid":12583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"[多圖多片] 7.7 克警資料整合 (重開)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1294615\" data-auto-link target=\